{"tid":1547403,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請歐頌賢立即將大學選區還給任嘉兒","createTime":"2019-09-06T16:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T22:07:26.000Z","uid":144108,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9be9a62226099b379968e340c71edb707f348be","tid":1547403,"uid":144108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"請歐頌賢立即將大學選區還給任嘉兒<br />\n<br />\n作者：楊文俊<br />\n<br />\n筆者在中西區居住近二十年，從小到大，都看到新世紀論壇的陳捷貴在附近的大學選區作威作福。陳捷貴自大學選區設立以來，雖政績乏善可陳，但卻礙於缺乏競爭，每次均僥幸地成功連任。<br />\n<br />\n在感動全港的反送中運動帶動下，曾任港大學生會內務副會長的任嘉兒，在大學選區。我們可以清楚看見，年輕的地區工作者，普遍更受街坊歡迎。同時，任因為曾在港大學生會擔當要職，與社區的聯繫密切，加上與民主派一眾立法會講員關係良好，受到民主派大力支持。其可以說是大學選區難得的新希望，極有可能在11月24日的選舉攆走陳捷貴。<br />\n<br />\n可是，身為「反自動當選運動」成員的歐頌賢，卻在任嘉兒小姐開始落區後，突然宣佈「積極考慮」參選，更以蠻橫無理的態度，霸道地迫走深受居民支持的任嘉兒小姐，使街坊無法選擇代表他們的代表，行為不能為大學選區，以至每一位中西區街坊接受！<br />\n<br />\n筆者素來尊重每一位願意服務社區的地區工作者，然而。作為中西區居民，本人不希望再看到陳捷貴再次連任。既然歐頌賢已通過whatsapp截圖講明自己之所以在任嘉兒小姐已「積極考慮」參選的情況下，依然「積極考慮」參選，是因為Tony Choi的意見，敬請歐頌賢面對民意，以大局為重，立即退出大學選區，將選區交回任嘉兒小姐「積極考慮」參選！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.me/jasonyeungmanchun\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fjasonyeungmanchun&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2oeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=2ae7cd76\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.me/jasonyeungmanchun</a><br />\n<br />\n如果各位覺得文章好看，可以讚好小弟臉書專頁，謝謝🙏🙏🙏"},{"pid":"e45c8d1bf8c6520b967e8cab6d7dffe9fcd4831d","tid":1547403,"uid":144108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:09:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4220139b30f933a0d7ec96b28a3694ed5503b0e8","tid":1547403,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Yw7YiF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Yw7YiF.jpg&h=e6c84b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日呀！冇人講呀 機場見</span>"},{"pid":"71850292f82462362f7997c7f2a1596fd749fef3","tid":1547403,"uid":144108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"661db0049e6ac0b1817decde0da131389490e655","tid":1547403,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806dfe5763c455d52de92cea4b1d9d1fdc61cc5a","tid":1547403,"uid":119271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返黎呀護士姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c7cf25d65c8138cf8976fdb2fe79bb12f6f7e8","tid":1547403,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"tony choi個肥佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4a323cb1f4fdbc039f7b7f6bb899f43a9b66e5","tid":1547403,"uid":296571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:31:25.000Z","msg":"推, 同埋叫任嘉兒企硬 撤回佢退選既決定!!!"},{"pid":"7bb55857430bf1c0a30973e5104052ba149c7e03","tid":1547403,"uid":144108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T22:07:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}